(We now find the formula for $a_n=a_{n-1}-a_{n-2}\sqrt{3}$ by defining the generating function $f(t)=\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}a_nt^n$.) Then, multiplying $a_{n-2}\sqrt{3}$ by $3$ and adding, we have
\begin{align*}
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}a_{n-1}3a_n\sqrt{3}&=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}a_{n-2}3^2a_n\\
\end{align*}

Then, placing the equations into each other, we have found the general formula for $a_n=\frac{-3a_{n-2}^2+3^{n-1}}{2-\sqrt{3}}$ Fix $n>1$.
