&=\cdots\\
&=\frac{-3\binom{-3}{50}a_0^2(-3)^{51}+3^{100}}{\left(-\frac{3}{2-\sqrt{3}}\right)^{50}\left(2-\sqrt{3}\right)}\\
&=\frac{426396085532285437811526478225969}{19} =\boxed{231867217573631303969083644943612}\tag*{$\blacksquare$}
